{"tid":2401461,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼公主最西格，最cheap排行榜，第一係佢！！","createTime":"2021-02-09T18:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T12:15:43.000Z","uid":219635,"like":12,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"66697bf57b079152b33842d35daa397888a865e6","tid":2401461,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:03:57.000Z","msg":"第一名：灰姑娘。格賤淫西，明明後母俾地方佢住，叫做有瓦遮頭，唔賣佢去做奴婢已經叫有養育之恩。對佢好似屋企人咁樣俾佢飲飲食食，供養長大，只係叫佢做下打掃同幫補家務，咁就厭三厭四，你唔係親生都算係咁啦。<br />\n而且貪錢拜金，又唔睇下自己咩身份，一日到黑想飛上枝頭變鳳凰，一朝得意。<br />\n最後更用盡一切方法，不擇手段地去達到目的，成功之後就扮可憐博同情攞光環，逼害同清算自己人。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">而且灰姑娘故事中：貧窮人努力向上，以西脫貧嘅故事更對後世尤其港女的育成及影響深遠。令人人都想釣金龜，以搵白馬王子為人生目標。</span><br />\n當中：港女梁詠琪更以身作則，唱出灰姑娘成名，而佢最後得償所願般，像灰姑娘一樣嫁到俾有錢洋人。<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇第二，第三名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d3340291b5cac3f82b6ad59b8710729d45a986","tid":2401461,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30623f7f812dafd2ba3386bf3185c0788a98992","tid":2401461,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436fd4ac1f54872baf7e49f63636a0715b154ac5","tid":2401461,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc5037f5b366a6bfc3adfab29187a6469865fe6","tid":2401461,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk